---
alwaysApply: true
---
NEVER add tool attribution to git commit messages, pull request titles,
or pull request descriptions. This includes but is not limited to:
- "Co-authored-by: Cursor" trailers
- "Made-with: Cursor" trailers  
- "Made with [Cursor](...)" markdown attributions
- "Generated with", "Built with", "Powered by" attributions
- Any link to cursor.com
- Similar attributions for Copilot, Claude, or any other AI tool
The author and the entire content is the human running the commit. Full stop.